    <string name="user_guide">User guide</string>
    <string name="user_guide_content">📱 Quick Start\n\n• First time: Tap the wallpaper button (top-right), select a video, then apply it in system settings\n• Quick switch: Tap any video card in history or local library to instantly switch wallpaper (no restart needed)\n\n🎬 Video Management\n\n• History: Automatically saves applied wallpapers, tap to quickly switch\n• Long press: Long press history cards to delete unwanted records\n• Local library: Horizontal scroll at bottom to browse all device videos\n• Show/Hide: Tap bottom button or swipe left to expand video library\n\n🎨 Personalization\n\n• Theme switch: 4 beautiful themes in sidebar (Classic/Modern/Elegant/Vibrant)\n• Follow system: Auto-adapt to system dark/light mode when enabled\n• Audio control: Enable video sound playback in settings\n• Hide icon: Hide app icon from launcher if desired\n\n💡 Pro Tips\n\n• Unlock fullscreen: Auto-play fullscreen video when device unlocks\n• Auto-hide: Set video library auto-hide timer (5/10/15 seconds)\n• Manual input: Enter video file path directly in sidebar\n• Scroll hide: Video library auto-collapses when scrolling history\n\n❓ Troubleshooting\n\n• Videos not showing? Check storage permissions\n• Switch not working? First-time use requires applying in system settings\n• Having issues? Tap "Report issue" to send us feedback</string>
